name: Universe #248
description: Universe #248 - The ancient beast that was prisoned inside Trothetera was getting impatient with each rotation of the universe. It clawed from the core to be released, to feel the void in its face once again. One day it made a tear in the surface. It knew it's escape was close. Yet 248 reached the universe before it could escape. It merged with the universe. Now it helps the universe keep the beast imprisoned.
